full_text: Screened by NARA, 7/11/2023 SERNAL U.S. TREASURY DEPARTMENT INTERNAL REVENUE SERVICE SERVICE DISTRICT DIRECTOR LOS ANGELES, CALIFORNIA 90012- 53 P. 0.
